                                <h1 class="fs-4 fw-bold mb-3">Contact Us</h1>
                                <p>Thanks for visiting our independent HER TREES : PUZZLE DREAM guide. We are not part
                                    of Stone,
                                    the developer and publisher of the game, but we monitor this inbox daily to keep the
                                    page
                                    accurate and respectful.</p>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">General Support &amp; Corrections</h2>
                                <p>Email <a href="mailto:support@hertrees.co">support@hertrees.co</a> if you:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Spot outdated platform information, pricing, or availability details.</li>
                                    <li>Have accessibility notes or spoiler-free tips we should highlight for players.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>Need help finding the official storefronts for HER TREES releases.</li>
                                </ul>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">DMCA or Rights Questions</h2>
                                <p>For copyright or trademark concerns, message
                                    <a href="mailto:dmca@hertrees.co">dmca@hertrees.co</a>. Include the URL of the page
                                    in
                                    question, proof of ownership, and the best way to reach you. We only publish
                                    promotional
                                    copy, so removal requests are usually resolved within two business days.
                                </p>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Media &amp; Community Collaborations</h2>
                                <p>If you represent a fan translation group, accessibility collective, or press outlet
                                    that
                                    covers HER TREES, email <a href="mailto:press@hertrees.co">press@hertrees.co</a>
                                    with a brief
                                    summary of your project so we can point visitors to your work when appropriate.</p>

                                <p class="mt-3 small text-secondary">Please note: For refunds, gameplay bugs, or other
                                    issues
                                    with the official release, contact Stone directly through the store where you
                                    purchased HER
                                    TREES : PUZZLE DREAM. We only maintain this informational page.</p>
